attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay
Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: A renovated home in South Boston’s highly desirable City Point. Just 2 blocks from the beach, within a recently repointed, classic red brick rowhouse, this chic condo features an efficient floor plan with 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom and an approx. 400sf private backyard complete with a large 3 tiered deck. The home’s open concept kitchen/living space features a shiplap accent wall and sleek grey flat paneled cabinetry, Carrera-like quartz countertops, a geometric white subway tiled backsplash and stainless steel appliances. The bathroom also features a stylish remodel and the expansive bedroom has plenty of space for a queen size bed and desk/home office space, and boasts a walk-in closet and direct access to the private outdoor space. This home is complete with in-unit laundry and custom plantation shutters on all windows and matte black fixtures/accents throughout to enhance the cohesiveness of the home’s design aesthetic.
